values: Some People really annoy me with the drama. I mean come on!!!

Today i was supposed to go to softball practice in the morning at 8:30! But my mom wakes me up and says "DON'T YOU HAVE SOFTBALL PRACTICE TODAY!?"...AND ITS LIKE 9:45... SO YEAH...

After that little episode my mother and i went to the bank. It took like forever for the line to get through. But we got our money and were on our way to Zorbas. After we were done there we went to A.J. Right. I love it there.

At A.j. Right i got a purse, water jug for softball and poka dotted flip flops! ;) When we were about to be rung up, this lady who just changed her name(because she got married) well her credit card wasnt working because of that, so the line took like 15 MINUTES to get through and she was only buying like one thing! But we EVENTUALLY got out of that ordeal.

 

So on to CVS mother andf i went;) I got some pHisoderm heat scrub that Kim introduced me to (thanks kimberly! ;) )! And then i was done with that.

On to Kelly's finally! When i got there we hung out for a bit then we rented Euro-Trip, and t h i r t e e n . It was cool. So here i am typing in the journal. Thanks Nicole for the new Layout ;)

Paige*

Today i just got up from sleeping and cleaned... Boooring...

After that i went to my softball game at 6:30. We beat Trenton like 16 to 6. It was cool.

2morrow im going to kelly's so that should be fun. Update then. bye.

After school was over there wasnt much to do:( But then Kimberly Ottoni called me and we went to eat at the mall, and got some BLING BLING! lol. We saw some guy who oddly enough looked EXACTLY like Simon Colwell. WEEEEIRD!

Then after the mall we went to Kimmy Poo's house and hung out. Her mom drove us to chart hits to get a movie but we ended up going to sav-on and buying food (the bag broke, RIGHT when we were on her grass in front of her house, GrRrRr!). Then we watched MTV movie awards, they were gay. Then i went home about like 10:30 or 11:00, i dont remember.

That was day one. ;)
